          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/blog/getting-started-ml" class="blog-card">
          <div class="blog-card-image" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ff9a9e 0%, #fecfef 100%);"></div>
          <div class="blog-card-content">
            <h3 class="blog-card-title">Getting Started with Machine Learning: A Beginner's Guide</h3>
            <p class="blog-card-excerpt">Everything you need to know to start your machine learning journey.</p>
            <div class="blog-card-meta">December 5, 2025 • 12 min read</div>
          </div>
        </a>

        <a href="/blog/ai-healthcare" class="blog-card">
          <div class="blog-card-image" style="background: linear-gradient(135deg, #ffecd2 0%, #fcb69f 100%);"></div>
          <div class="blog-card-content">
            <h3 class="blog-card-title">AI in Healthcare: Transforming Patient Care</h3>
            <p class="blog-card-excerpt">Discover how AI is improving diagnosis, treatment, and patient outcomes.</p>
            <div class="blog-card-meta">November 30, 2025 • 11 min read</div>
          </div>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
